                        <p>GameStop understands that you care about your privacy and we are committed to being transparent about how we collect, use, store, and disclose your Personal Information. This privacy policy (""Privacy Policy"") describes the information we collect about you, how it is used and to whom it is disclosed and explains the rights and choices you have to control how we handle your Personal Information.</p>
